pesquisaveis.valor: coalesce(pf.nome, pj.razaosocial, (select coalesce(pfcmc.nome, pjcmc.razaosocial) from pessoa p left join pessoafisica pfcmc on pfcmc.id = p.id left join pessoajuridica pjcmc on pjcmc.id = p.id where p.id = ce.pessoa_id), (select coalesce(pfcmc.nome, pjcmc.razaosocial) from propriedade p left join pessoafisica pfcmc on pfcmc.id = p.pessoa_id left join pessoajuridica pjcmc on pjcmc.id = p.pessoa_id where p.imovel_id = ci.id and current_date between p.iniciovigencia and coalesce(p.finalvigencia, current_date) FETCH FIRST 1 ROW ONLY), (select coalesce(pfcmc.nome, pjcmc.razaosocial) from propriedaderural p left join pessoafisica pfcmc on pfcmc.id = p.pessoa_id left join pessoajuridica pjcmc on pjcmc.id = p.pessoa_id where p.imovel_id = cr.id and current_date between p.iniciovigencia and coalesce(p.finalvigencia, current_date) FETCH FIRST 1 ROW ONLY))

coalesce(pf.cpf, pj.cnpj, (select coalesce(pfcmc.cpf, pjcmc.cnpj) from pessoa p left join pessoafisica pfcmc on pfcmc.id = p.id left join pessoajuridica pjcmc on pjcmc.id = p.id where p.id = ce.pessoa_id), (select coalesce(pfcmc.cpf, pjcmc.cnpj) from propriedade p left join pessoafisica pfcmc on pfcmc.id = p.pessoa_id left join pessoajuridica pjcmc on pjcmc.id = p.pessoa_id where p.imovel_id = ci.id and current_date between p.iniciovigencia and coalesce(p.finalvigencia, current_date) FETCH FIRST 1 ROW ONLY), (select coalesce(pfcmc.cpf, pjcmc.cnpj) from propriedaderural p left join pessoafisica pfcmc on pfcmc.id = p.pessoa_id left join pessoajuridica pjcmc on pjcmc.id = p.pessoa_id where p.imovel_id = cr.id and current_date between p.iniciovigencia and coalesce(p.finalvigencia, current_date) FETCH FIRST 1 ROW ONLY))

from:
from solicitacaodoctooficial sdo
left join documentooficial doc on sdo.documentooficial_id = doc.id
inner join tipodoctooficial tdo on sdo.tipodoctooficial_id = tdo.id
left join cadastroimobiliario ci on sdo.cadastroimobiliario_id = ci.id
left join cadastroeconomico ce on sdo.cadastroeconomico_id = ce.id
left join cadastrorural cr on sdo.cadastrorural_id = cr.id
left join pessoafisica pf on sdo.pessoafisica_id = pf.id
left join pessoajuridica pj on sdo.pessoajuridica_id = pj.id
where sdo.situacaosolicitacao = 'CANCELADO'
